= javascript_include_tag 'application'

%section
  %h2 Introduction
  %p{style: "padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px;"}
    MeeScan is a patron-initiated self-checkout application for library materials.
    The data below captures individual checkout sessions recorded by MeeScan kiosks,
    including device information, item counts, and receipt preferences.

%hr

%section
  %h2 Resources
  %h3 Database Access
  %p{style: "padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px;"}
    For those connecting directly to the PostgreSQL database or using the report
    export tool, MeeScan tables use the prefix
    %code meescan_

  %h3 Data Tables
  %ul
    - resources.each do |resource|
      %li= link_to resource.resource_name.human, "/mee_scan/#{resource.resource_name.param_key.pluralize}"
